o-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lwg1665702675989.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lwg1665702675989.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lwg1665702675989.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lwg1665702675989\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                           \n Margins\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Margins of the printed output are expressed in terms of lines and\n      characters.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lwg1665702675989__li_d4481e1_d4482e1_d4483e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Left Margin</span>—number of character positions for the left margin. The default is 0.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lwg1665702675989__li_d4484e1_d4485e1_d4486e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Right Margin</span>—position of the right margin as measured in character positions from the left edge of the page, not from the left margin.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lwg1665702675989__li_d4487e1_d4488e1_d4489e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Top Margin</span>—line where printing should start on each page. The default is 0.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lwg1665702675989__li_d4490e1_d4491e1_d4492e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Bottom Margin</span>—number of lines from the bottom of the page where a page eject should be inserted.\n <p class=\"p\" id=\"lwg1665702675989__p_d9809e1_d9810e1_d9811e1\">This also controls whether Uniface will insert a form feed (non-blank value required) or default to the printer (blank value). It is recommended that you enter a value of at least <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529763\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529763\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Margins Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Margins Margins of the printed output are expressed in terms of lines and characters. Left Margin —number of character positions for the left margin. The default is 0. Right Margin —position of the right margin as measured in character positions from the left edge of the page, not from the left margin. Top Margin —line where printing should start on each page. The default is 0. Bottom Margin —number of lines from the bottom of the page where a page eject should be inserted. This also controls whether Uniface will insert a form feed (non-blank value required) or default to the printer (blank value). It is recommended that you enter a value of at least 1 . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}